title: Yuusha, Yamemasu
alternative_titles: I Will Quit Being the Hero
author: Quantum
synopsis:
Quantum ini bercerita tentang
After saving the world, the strongest hero, Leo, has nowhere else to go. His overly strong power is something that a peaceful world doesn't need. The place where he ends up working is his former enemy, the Demon Queen's Army! This is the comic version of the Japanese novel which won one of the major online prizes for novels!---    [Original Web Novel](https://kakuyomu.jp/works/1177354054882385011) (Raw)
